The Special Adviser to Governor Aminu Waziri Tambuwal of Sokoto State on Media and Publicity, Malam Imam Imam is dead. Imam died around 3.am on Friday at the Nziamye Turkish Hospital, Abuja, after a brief illness. The younger brother, Abubakar Imam, and his friend, Muhammad Isa, confirmed that the deceased would be buried at Wuse 2, Abuja, after Juma’at prayers. The burial would be held at the Al-Nur Mosque in Abuja. The Sokoto State Government has yet to release an official statement on the death of the governor’s spokesman. 